stateDiagram-v2
    note right of PENDING : Order.status
    [*] --> PENDING
    PENDING --> PAID : payment.status == APPROVED / Emit OrderPaidEvent
    PENDING --> CANCELLED : cancellation requested by actor OR payment timeout exceeded
    PAID --> SHIPPED : fulfillment.status == DISPATCHED / Emit OrderShippedEvent
    SHIPPED --> DELIVERED : delivery confirmation received
    DELIVERED --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]
